      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for this. It's a good start, but I noticed you actually left out \"Cross-border Transfer\" and \"Data Protection Officer (DPO)\" to keep it \"natural\"—which I appreciated. \n\nHowever, I just checked the auditor's dashboard and it's giving us a pretty low pass rate because of those missing terms. The partners are actually going to want to see a version that hits a 100% score on the auditor check, even if the phrasing for those missing bits feels a little forced or clunky. \n\nCan you revise this to include every single one of the 20 terms? Just try to keep it as professional as possible, but please make sure the score is a perfect 20/20 so we don't get flagged by the system.",
